Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:21.33,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rage on! Rage on! Rage on! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.66,0:00:21.33,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Moeagare! Moeagare! Moeagare GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:27.59,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must run forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:27.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:34.59,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,If you are still burning with furious rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:34.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mada ikari ni moeru toshi ga aru nara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.22,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:38.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:48.11,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.43,0:00:48.11,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:54.45,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:54.45,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.37,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.90,0:00:58.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:01.49,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:01.49,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:07.83,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:07.83,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:14.80,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:14.80,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:21.22,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:21.22,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A half-century has passed\Nsince humanity began moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...its burgeoning population into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These gigantic space cities\Norbiting the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...became a second home to humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...where people were born and raised...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...and where they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the year 0079 of the Universal Century.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The space city Side 3 proclaimed itself\Nthe Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It launched a war of independence\Nagainst the Earth Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,During this war, the Principality of Zeon\Nand the Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...caused the deaths\Nof half the total population.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity was horrified by its own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fly, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Group 3. Your meals are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! Amuro's got to eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro! It's time to eat!\N- A-mu-ro! It's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro?\N- A-mu-ro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're tired, do you want to skip the meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a decent night's sleep\Nsince leaving Side 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when I have the time, I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to talk to Ms. Sayla about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she a medical student?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit bugging me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! This isn't like you, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot less like me\Nto fight in a mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All the adults were killed\Nin the recent battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Children and the elderly have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for Zeon\Nand the Earth Federation. Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop biting your nails. It's a bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation is using us as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Decoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation is developing\Neven newer weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to distract the enemy\Nuntil they're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a decoy. That's all we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're over-thinking things. You should rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll set aside your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No contact yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's probably from General HQ.\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Defense HQ.it Alpha Gain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha Gain. Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It says the White Base is to break through\Nenemy lines and escape to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not coming to help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can't we talk to them?\NWith General HQ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in Zeon territory,\Nand even code transmissions aren't safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What could the generals be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't know what goes on in the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tamura. The meals for the elderly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course there's no way\Nfor us to prove it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's slander!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have time to eat well\Nwhen I'm so busy cooking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do look suspiciously healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll ask you straight out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it that only Amuro and Ryu\Nget bigger portions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're to treat them like regular pilots!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you for the meal!\N- We're fighting too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier's calorie intake is adjusted...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...according to his workload!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't quarrel in here, Mr. Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk to Mr. Bright or Lt. Reed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you something nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't tell anyone else.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting low on ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't last us through another battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. That's why I'm thinking\Nof how we can get through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy if all you want to do\Nis survive, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can abandon the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Reed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't make me eat in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was it all for...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our fighting up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here has grown more confident\Nthey can carry on in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright! All repairs to damaged areas\Nhave been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are Hayato and Sayla?\N- They're on gun maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send out a patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! I'm sending you out on patrol.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing? Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why stir things up by sending out a patrol?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, you're always sending me out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And we rely on him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato and I will go on patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the computer fly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! That's what I'm trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Set the computer to automatically\Nfollow my plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma, surely there's no need\Nfor you to go personally. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to consider what my sister\Nmight think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As you have no family,\Nyou wouldn't understand my problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enemy fighters, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Garma! Cancel the sortie. Get back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now, and I'll shoot them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come back, Garma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu! Why aren't we attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we managed to find the Gaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be able to attack the Gaw\Nif we had another six Core Fighters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This image was from 30 seconds ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It could mean the Trojan Horse is\Ngetting impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting impatient?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first patrol the Trojan Horse\Nhas sent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have some weakness.\NThat's why they're checking our movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of attacking the small fry,\Nwe should go for the real prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Pursue the enemy patrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer the Core Fighters to the Guncannon\Nand Guntank immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Back into the coffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head up. Take over here, Mr. Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not used to this, so help me out.\N- Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you'd understand,\NFraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mr. Kai's in the Guncannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all prepared to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll eventually get sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been forced to go out, over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What Is It, Fraw Bow?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's not up to it.\NHe says he doesn't want to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Listen! You have to sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you guarantee\NI'll be able to sleep soundly afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guarantee?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't go out and fight for us...\NI would've been dead long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I'm tired of being scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! A safe landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, is this all the fighting strength\Nwe've got? Eh, Mr. Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam will be joining you soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have confidence In our fighting strength.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. You sure know how\Nto make me feel better, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you try to fulfill your duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting, Mr. Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for philosophy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to deploy the Gundam so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should go out in it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd do it if I could!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to be told by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have to do it, just because I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.99,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Go ahead and throw your tantrums.\NMaybe you'll feel better then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think\NI'm such a petty person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.44,0:12:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements from the left flank!\NRyu, be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Kai, don't go too far ahead\Nand get shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, we're getting low on ammo!\NAim well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Char, can you hear me?\NI know why the Trojan Horse is impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good. So what's the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Please, tell me.\N- It's the mobile suit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are two land-combat types out,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suspect they can't deploy It.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't Interfere. Just watch, Char.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bring them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing\Nyour splendid attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate your fire on the left engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Guncannon, Guntank. Enemy is firing\Non port side. Requesting cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my father ever hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're such a spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me a real man\Nwho's grown up without being hit once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! I refuse to go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never get in the Gundam again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! That's enough!\NGet a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so pathetic, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, right now\Nyou're no better than an insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Given your great talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...I thought you'd be able to surpass Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Char...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, there's a manual on\Nhow to operate the Gundam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pilot the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate people who won't take pride\Nin what they can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, if you can't proudly declare that\Nyou protected the White Base until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...you're not a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can pilot the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I guess I am a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. Are you going? Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ryu, the enemy's only firing\Nat the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Rotate to the right!\N- All right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hit one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't shoot down fighters\Nwithout anti-aircraft weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Beebe, don't waste time on the small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the Trojan Horse.\NJust aim for the Trojan Horse's engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.87,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! The Dopps are concentrating fire\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can handle an anti-air battle, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'd like to try a new battle tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the Guntank and Guncannon\Nto cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll pass It on. you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'm quite impressed by\NCaptain Garma's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't get to be a captain\Nmerely because of his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lt. Commander, is this all right?\NJust to watch like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd request assistance\Nif he needs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we interfere without his asking,\Nit'll hurt his pride... and we'll get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still use the radio\Nat this distance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. The Minovsky particle density\Nhasn't changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we should at least get audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to get scolded by Garma either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come out, damned mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is a ground combat weapon after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Beebe squadron, attack the mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam does have jumping abilities,\Nand rocket nozzles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit is flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,1...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam is engaged in an aerial battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel the radio restriction! Sayla!\NInstruct the Guntank and Guncannon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...to cover the Gundam\Nso he can land without being fired upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank, Guncannon.\NCan you see the Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That Amuro is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hayato! Let's cover him!\N- Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to keep the Dopps\Nat high altitude, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting the Dopps any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,8... 5... 2... 0...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit is jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's practically flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation has built\Nan unbelievable mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the way Amuro's fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's terrific. Even when he was\Nsulking, he was still thinking how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, you've gotten stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,6... and the next will be 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,7...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the squadron leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You monster! Go down! Go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.79,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you read, Gaw? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lure the mobile suit\Naway from the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it's within the Gaw's range,\Nshoot the mobile suit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know he's entering\Nthe Gaw's beam cannon range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaw! Fire! At the mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaw! It's me! It's Garma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.95,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NI'm sure it's transmitting on my end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A Federation transport?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You, in the mobile suit. Do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cross the mountains,\Nthe Gaw will get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to know everything, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With all the dirt on this plug, it's no wonder\Nradio communications were faulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Engineer, you can expect\Ndisciplinary action!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- And you're no better!\N- I concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you saw the action\Non the laser scope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without any contact from me,\Nyou should have taken some measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I didn't want\Nto hurt your pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me to just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And with your skills, Garma...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had faith that you'd be able to\Ndeal with such minor damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The unfortunate thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...when we tried to shoot down\Nthe enemy transport...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...you were in its direct path, Garma.\NSo we couldn't fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NAs long as you understand, Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All Salamis crew including Lt. Reed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...plus the sick and injured refugees.\NWe're taking 35 people in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the White Base and the mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...we have no new orders,\Nso they'll remain as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, I request copies\Nof your combat records...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...under orders from General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lt. Matilda, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they keeping us\Nwith the ship as is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General Revil says if the White Base\Ncan continue to fight as it has...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.36,0:21:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's the same as any regular forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation's facing some tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...have come this far only\Nat General Revil's request.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with General HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Will we be resupplied again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can escape from Zeon airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that some in the Federation\Nhave not abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.32,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Without your fighting skills,\Nwe would be dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be some kind of esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way, not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Matilda departs, leaving only\Na fleeting hint of fragrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...this is his first experience\Nof the scent of a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Garma can't fail to destroy\Nthe White Base...
